# Trader Dashboard — Free Data API Keys
# Get your free API keys from:
#   Twelve Data: https://twelvedata.com (800 calls/day free)
#   Finnhub:     https://finnhub.io   (60 calls/min free)
#
# Set these in a .env file (not .env.example) for live data.
# Without them, the app falls back to mock data automatically.

# VITE_TWELVEDATA_KEY=your_key_here
# VITE_FINNHUB_KEY=your_key_here
